[style]
do GameManager.change_selfie_cam("Player")
Player: Still keeping the shop?
do GameManager.change_selfie_cam("StorePerson")
StoreOwner2: For now. But I saw two men loitering out front, scribbling in notebooks. Makes everyone anxious, customers don't like it.
do GameManager.change_selfie_cam("Player")
Player: Want me to talk to them.
do GameManager.change_selfie_cam("StorePerson")
StoreOwner2: You're in enough trouble with them as is. I dont want you getting in more on my behalf.